RAWALPINDI, Aug 01 (APP):Pakistan Army on Monday pledged its share of two days rations to flood affected population in Balochistan, Sindh, Southern Punjab, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa (KP) and Gilgit Baltistan.
The subject relief items including Flour, Sugar, Rice, Tea , Cooking Oil , Milk Powder and pulses  would be distributed by Army Formations to flood victims in different areas, an Inter Services Public Relations (ISPR) news release said.
